OL,3,C'I wanted to die': Warning from boy
OL,4,Cset on fire while playing
OL,6,FWarning: This article contains images
OL,7,Fof Hunter Jory's burn injuries
OL,9,FA boy who said he "wanted to die"
OL,10,Fafter being engulfed in flames has
OL,11,Fwarned other young people about the
OL,12,Fdangers of playing with fire.
OL,14,FHunter Jory, 12, from Sheffield,
OL,15,Fsuffered horrific burn injuries after
OL,16,Fa fire in a field exploded when a
OL,17,Ffriend threw a petrol can onto the
OL,18,Fflames.
