OL,3,C'I wanted to die': Warning from boy
OL,4,Cset on fire while playing
OL,6,FHunter, who has already had skin
OL,7,Fgrafts and will need operations into
OL,8,Fadulthood, said: "I felt like I wanted
OL,9,Fto die. It hurt really bad."
OL,11,FHis mum, Kim, called on other parents
OL,12,Fto educate their children.
OL,14,FShe said: "Make your kids aware of the
OL,15,Fdangers of fires, because I don't want
OL,16,Fany other child or parent to go
OL,17,Fthrough what we're going through."
