OL,3,C'I wanted to die': Warning from boy
OL,4,Cset on fire while playing
OL,6,FHunter was playing with friends in a
OL,7,Ffield near Dinnington High School on
OL,8,F18 August when one of them started a
OL,9,Ffire.
OL,11,FHe was rapidly engulfed in flames
OL,12,Fafter fuel was thrown, but used the
OL,13,F"stop, drop and roll" technique he had
OL,14,Fbeen taught to try to minimise the
OL,15,Feffects.
OL,17,FHe managed to run to a friend's house
OL,18,Fand Kim was called.
