OL,3,C'I wanted to die': Warning from boy
OL,4,Cset on fire while playing
OL,6,FShe said: "My instant reaction was
OL,7,Fhe'd been tipped off his push bike or
OL,8,Fhe's been clipped or something normal
OL,9,Flike that, but obviously outside the
OL,10,Fhouse he was still screaming that he
OL,11,Fwas on fire."
OL,13,FKim, 38, rushed her son to the nearby
OL,14,Fdoctor's surgery, where Hunter was
OL,15,Fdoused with water and given a cannula
OL,16,Fas they waited for an ambulance.
OL,18,FHe was taken to Sheffield Children's
OL,19,FHospital where he had to have skin
OL,20,Fgrafts on his leg, head, hands and
OL,21,Fneck. He continues to be treated there.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
