OL,3,C'I wanted to die': Warning from boy
OL,4,Cset on fire while playing
OL,6,FKim said she "cried my heart out"
OL,7,Fwatching him go through the pain of
OL,8,Fhealing and the emotions that come
OL,9,Fwith it.
OL,11,FChris Tyler, group manager at South
OL,12,FYorkshire Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,13,Fsaid there was a "big spike" in
OL,14,Fincidents of anti-social fires at this
OL,15,Ftime of year.
OL,17,FHe added: "In the UK each year we have
OL,18,Fwell over 300,000 deliberate fires
OL,19,Faccounting for around one third of the
OL,20,Ffires we attend.
